== Summary ==
Screenshot taken from the video on Youtube “VRChat Rewind 2019” by Nekko State.
Url: https://youtu.be/C1NK-zireUg?si=4mB39C4KOtxjYZjN&t=817

Discord: nekobueno

This image is used with explicit permission from the creator (“Go for it!”), 
who allowed the inclusion of a single frame from the video for documentation 
purposes on the VRChat Wiki.

This screenshot shows the Studio Ghibli World as it appeared in VRChat Rewind 2019, 
highlighting its presence in the community that year. The mention of the Rewind 
was originally shared by ElvenStrider, a member of the world’s development team, 
while recounting the history of the project.

